    <h3>Cracking</h3>
    <p>
        - Hydrocarbons can be brown down (cracked) to produce smaller more useful molecules.<br>
        - <code>C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>22</sub> → C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>12</sub> + C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>8</sub> + C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>4</sub></code><br>
        - The products made are more useful than the starting hydrocarbons.
    </p>
